        "text": "LTEOTADM134The DevDetail subtree shall be as defined in theOMA Device Management  Standardized Objects V1.2.The Device shall implement the following node values of the DevDetail  subtree:\nNote: APN Management and ADD flowrequires that ./DevDetail/FwV be an implemented and  populated leaf node.",
