        "section_number": "1.5.3",
        "title": "Firmware Over The Air (FOTA)",
        "text": "The device must support over the air software update. Open Access and Open Development device vendors  may use their own FOTA system to update device software (firmware) over the air or use the Verizon Wireless  FOTA system. To obtain more information about Verizon FOTA Service, contact VZW.FOTA- Services@VerizonWireless.com.",
