      "text": "LTEOTADM131The device shall support the following basenode and sub-tree nodes for DM operations. * DDF provided by the DeviceOEMs contains all information needed for the OMA-DM nodes.\n./ManagedObjects Root Node for all Managed Object items\n1.5.1.3.6.1Factory Data Reset Persistence\nAll values in the DM trees (DMACC, DevInfo, DevDetail, ManagedObjects) listed in this document  shall persist through a Factory Data Reset unless otherwise specified.\n1.5.1.3.6.2Reset to Original Values\nAll values in the DM trees (DMACC, DevInfo, DevDetail, ManagedObjects) shall be reset to their original values in  the current binary upon software flash with the service support tool or OEM provided APK.",
