        "chunk_text": "[MNO: VZW | Release: 2026_feb | Plan: Reqs-LTE_OTADM | Version: 46]\n[Path: OTA-DM SPECIFICATIONS > COMMON REQUIREMENTS FOR OTADM - STANDARDS > OTADM TRANSPORT SECURITY REQUIREMENTS]\n[Req ID: VZ_REQ_LTEOTADM_4105999311947510]\n\nOTADM TRANSPORT SECURITY REQUIREMENTS\nDue to recent security vulnerability with SSL transport layer protocols, the device must only support  TLS transport layer protocol (version 1.2 & higher). It is recommended that device vendors provide the  ability to install additional root certificates over the air if a need arise.\n\u2022 Device vendors must support SHA-256 SSL server certificates.\n\u2022 Device vendor must use below URL for their new devices and SUs which supports SHA-256  SSL server certificates.\n./DMAcc/AppAddr/Port 443\n| ./DMAcc/AppAddr/Addr | https://4g3.vzwdm.com |\n| --- | --- |\n| ./DMAcc/AppAddr/AddrType | URI |\n| ./DMAcc/AppAddr/Port | 443 |\n[Image: 1.5.1.3 OTADM TRANSPORT SECURITY REQUIREMENTS VZ_REQ_LTEOTADM_22983]",
